{
  "stem": "1222.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Should I start talking?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After three months-- that's 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's approximately would be probably around May 1945-- May 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was still in Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war was still going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would say approximately-- I would say in Lviv.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's about 300 miles from [NON-ENGLISH] 345 miles from Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was still the war going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could hear a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What happened there-- I was already fully in Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I took a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could take any Jewish house I wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The police made sure-- it was like a little government-- that I could take any house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I wanted to stay near the police station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Munich ?] wasn't the police station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They used to come over to sleep over when it wasn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What-- Then after that, I saw sooner or later, they don't want to have any witnesses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were the only one, two Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They going to kill us, sooner or later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I went away, and I spoke to the-- to the chief of the police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He made me up papers that I was born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I-- in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's not Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's still Russia there because if you want to go to Poland, you've got to go up through close to Lviv.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then later on, maybe close to whatever you want to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lviv started already Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Russia ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He made me up papers that I could go away legally But he tried to talk me out of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a reason why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not because-- it's a matter of fact I think one of his next-- the chief of police were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was talking to me Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed more witnesses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed more [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
